text: Midhurst is a market town and civil parish in Chichester District, West Sussex, England. Midhurst may also refer to: * Midhurst (electoral division), West Sussex, England * Midhurst (UK electoral ward), West Sussex, England * Midhurst (UK Parliament constituency), in existence from 1311 to 1885 * Midhurst (LSWR) railway station, open from 1864 to 1925 * Midhurst railway station, open from 1866 to 1964 * Midhurst, Ontario, Canada ==See also== * Midhirst, Taranaki, New Zealand, often misspelled Midhurst
title: Midhurst (disambiguation)
